title: BOOK CLUB: Colton Haynes Talks Miss Memory Lane
itunes:title: BOOK CLUB: Colton Haynes Talks Miss Memory Lane
description:
In a special Book Club episode of Everything Iconic, Danny welcomes author/actor Colton Haynes to talk about his new memoir, Miss Memory Lane. They also get into his acting work (Teen Wolf/Arrow), modeling, and more!


NOTE: We also discuss mental health and sexual abuse as is detailed in the book.


BOOK: Smarturl.it/unremember
